Learn CRM Analytics with Trailhead

Trailhead is the fun and free way to learn Salesforce. Get acquainted with CRM Analytics through Trailhead using a special CRM Analytics-enabled Developer Edition org.

For the CRM Analytics trails, you canâ€™t use an old Developer Edition org. You must sign up for the special Developer Edition that comes with a limited CRM Analytics license and contains sample data required for the CRM Analytics trails.
